{
  "id": "RAW_e50e6c2e",
  "title": "大模型哪里出问题、怎么修，这篇可解释性综述一次讲清",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651013833&idx=3&sn=c7c62fbe7666c0ffccaa99b4479f38ec",
  "date": "2026-01-27 04:00:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">过去几年，机制可解释性</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Mechanistic Interpretability）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">让研究者得以在 Transformer 这一 “黑盒” 里追踪信息如何流动、表征如何形成：从单个神经元到注意力头，再到跨层电路。但在很多场景里，研究者真正关心的不只是 “模型为什么这么答”，还包括 “能不能更稳、更准、更省，更安全”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">正是在这一背景下，来自</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">香港大学、</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">复旦大学</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">、慕尼黑大学、曼切斯特大学、腾讯</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等机构的研究团队联合发布了&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">“可实践的机制可解释性”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Actio</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">nable</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;Mechanistic Interpretability）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">综述。文章通过&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">\"Locate, Steer, and Improve\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;的三阶段范式，系统梳理了如何将 MI 从 “显微镜” 转化为 “手术刀”，为大模型的对齐、能力增强和效率提升提供了一套具体的方法论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6844319775596073\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"713\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503529737\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=415c5ee3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadI3B7DLIp22XoCAvuxiaGOWicydmdDC0LH2nApTY5oYmCNO7fCKYknUaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：Locate, Steer, and Improve: A Practical Survey of Actionable Mechanistic Interpretability in Large Language Models</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.14004\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.14004</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">项目主页：<a href=\"https://github.com/rattlesnakey/Awesome-Actionable-MI-Survey\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/rattlesnakey/Awesome-Actionable-MI-Survey</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">从 “显微镜” 到 “手术刀” 的范式转移</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">尽管大语言模型（LLM）近年来在多种任务上展现出了强大的能力，但其内部的运作机制依然在很大程度上不透明，常被视为一个 “黑盒”。围绕如何理解这一黑盒，机制可解释性</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Mechanistic Interpretability, MI）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">逐渐发展为一个重要研究方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然而，现有的 MI 研究大多仍停留在 “</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">观察</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">” 层面：例如哪些神经元编码了特定实体、哪些注意力头参与了指代消解、哪些计算电路实现了算术或逻辑功能。但一个更关键的问题仍有待回答 —— 这些机制层面的发现，如何真正转化为模型行为和性能的实际改进？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">正是基于这一问题，研究团队撰写了这篇</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">以实践为导向的系统性综述</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。不同于传统综述侧重于回答 “模型内部有什么”，本文将关注点转向 “可以对模型做什么”，并围绕 \"</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">定位-&gt;操控-&gt;提升</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\" 这一闭环，系统梳理了机制可解释性如何走向可实践的模型改造路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5349913244650086\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1729\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503529739\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e961f14d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadND8W6GSLhMs61NVR3mgHLGFciblz9ab4llx2IFunSnbbCjeDtTneTZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">1. Locate：像医生一样精准 “定位” 病灶</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">干预的前提是准确的诊断。文章首先构建了一套</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">系统的可解释对象</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Interpretable Objects）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">定义与分类体系</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，为后续的机制分析奠定了基础。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">微观层面</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：从传统的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">神经元</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Neuron）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;到近年来广泛使用的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">稀疏自编码器特征</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（SAE Feature）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">宏观层面</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：涵盖</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">注意力头</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Attention Heads）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、残差流&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Residual Stream）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等组件。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">诊断工具</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：梳</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">理了</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">包括</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">因果归因</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Causal Attribution）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、探针</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Probing）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、梯度检测</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Gradient Detection）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等主流定位技术。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.772633744855967\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"972\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503529738\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=46630945&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadOG1FEsA2T8gkCxf6uutdIVE2eAkRewRjdVrRdnl5OPq1MmTiafPcLVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2. Steer：面向干预的 “手术” 手段</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当关键对象被定位出来之后，对其进行干预便成为可能。这也标志着机制可解释性从 “观察” 迈向 “可实践” 的关键一步。文章将现有的干预手段归纳为三大类：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">幅度操控</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Amplitude Manipulation）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：对目标对象进行置零/缩放/替换</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（ablation, scaling, patching）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">等操作，实现 “开关式” 或 “强度式” 控制。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">靶向优化</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Targeted Optimization）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：利用定位到的关键组件进行参数级的微调（如仅微调特定的 Attention Heads），比全量微调更高效、副作用更小。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">向量运算</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Vector Arithmetic）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：在激活空间中加入/移除任务向量或特征向量，实现推理时引导模型行为。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2890231621349446\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"993\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503529740\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9935c0f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadOIJxr9BxagUIEKNu3Ybnb1ALRCjxBHAwhVAeGaRcn0s4WciarqDOSWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3. Improve：MI 赋能的三大应用场景</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Application 章节中将其划分为三大类别，并逐一呈现了 MI 在这三个维度上的实质性提升：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">对齐</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Alignment）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：通过定位与有约束的干预，减少有害行为、降低幻觉或提升遵循指令的稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">能力</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Capability）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">把机理层面的 “功能模块”转化为具体的能力增强路径</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（例如更稳的推理、记忆或语言生成）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">效率</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Efficiency）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">探索更灵活的干预与压缩手段，为高效训练，推理加速与部署成本提供新抓手。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6188714153561518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1081\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503529741\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f699331&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiad0icAcn7GJFR2licOqbIsVNZHEdYWkIIsMnD9flpqcFepMYk1ezwWibeJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">【Paper List 指南】</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对相似领域的可解释性工作，研究团队将分散的研究成果做成了 “可检索的图表”：每篇论文都用统一标签标出它在研究什么、怎么找到关键位置、以及如何进一步用来引导模型行为，以便将不同研究路线的代表性工作进行直观对照，快速定位与自身需求最契合的的关键论文。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:flex;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;font-size:medium;padding-bottom:10px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;overflow-x:auto;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"width: 350px;max-width: 350px;scroll-snap-align: center;flex-shrink: 0;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0920060331825037\" data-w=\"663\" style=\"width: 350px;border-radius: 4px;vertical-align: top;display: block;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=388cd081&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadbnsvcUz9HLmrOgsLIvKvzbu8ZqFKZnWHleljWb7vKbMg7GzUQ8iaF1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <p style=\"width: 350px;max-width: 350px;scroll-snap-align: center;flex-shrink: 0;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3252840909090908\" data-w=\"704\" style=\"width: 350px;border-radius: 4px;vertical-align: top;display: block;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e06d229c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiad3z2CtfyoUP7uicAPaEwqWE6Jo9g7SwULHEOHAEcwJHNPIUiceiaR2QiaeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <p style=\"width: 350px;max-width: 350px;scroll-snap-align: center;flex-shrink: 0;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3163120567375886\" data-w=\"705\" style=\"width: 350px;border-radius: 4px;vertical-align: top;display: block;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80e84ff0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiad6JQnRPbRWZthbHr03KwmLas2icUH7u6umNngdyNjCwkhW4IH2ayyb3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <p style=\"width: 350px;max-width: 350px;scroll-snap-align: center;flex-shrink: 0;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.326241134751773\" data-w=\"705\" style=\"width: 350px;border-radius: 4px;vertical-align: top;display: block;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d346e6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiadpFibG2JU5AGibnAFE2nRVWchef98TvXftTykhUvc7N3uGVCLd3vbB8KA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <p style=\"width: 350px;max-width: 350px;scroll-snap-align: center;flex-shrink: 0;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7524475524475525\" data-w=\"715\" style=\"width: 350px;border-radius: 4px;vertical-align: top;display: block;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9df3b7a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8uYMdNaRAc4S0K5BxQVoiad7QN8soFHl3dzkokKPIMsQhibMc1RibkmU6VCy2RqzhbPUIjvWOjLvNEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 6px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">（左右滑动查看更多论文）</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">【结语】</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本综述通过 \"Locate-Steer-Improve\" 的框架，首次系统地勾勒出了 MI 从分析走向具体干预的路线图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">展望未来，作者团队认为 MI 的核心挑战与机遇在于打破 “各自为战” 的局面 —— 需要建立标准化的评估基准</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Standardized Evaluation）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，验证干预手段的泛化性；同时推动 MI 向自动化</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">（Automated MI）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">演进，最终实现让 AI 自主发现并修复内部错误的愿景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">期待这篇综述能为社区提供一份详实的 “指南”，推动大模型从不可解释的黑盒，真正走向透明、可控、可信的未来。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文系统梳理了机制可解释性（MI）从理论观察转向实践干预的“Locate-Steer-Improve”三阶段范式，旨在实现大模型的精准对齐、能力增强与效率提升。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文系统梳理了机制可解释性（MI）从理论观察转向实践干预的“Locate-Steer-Improve”三阶段范式，旨在实现大模型的精准对齐、能力增强与效率提升。",
  "summary": "这篇文章综述了由香港大学、复旦大学、腾讯等机构联合提出的“可实践的机制可解释性（Actionable MI）”研究框架。文章指出，机制可解释性研究正经历从“显微镜（仅观察）”到“手术刀（主动干预）”的范式转移。该框架分为三个核心阶段：首先是“定位（Locate）”，利用因果归因、探针等技术在神经元、SAE 特征及残差流等层面识别关键组件；其次是“操控（Steer）”，通过幅度操控、靶向优化和向量运算等手段干预模型行为；最后是“提升（Improve）”，将干预手段应用于模型对齐、能力增强及效率优化。综述还提供了结构化的论文列表，并展望了自动化 MI 及标准化评估的未来趋势，旨在推动大模型从黑盒走向透明可控。",
